* [[Javary River|Javary]]
* [[Jurua River|Jurua]]
* [[Madeira River|Madeira]]
* [[Marañón River|Marañón]]
* [[Morona]]
* [[Nanay River|Nanay]]
* [[Napo River|Napo]]
