* [[Tigre River|Tigre]]
* [[Tocantins River|Tocantins]]
* [[Trombetas]]
* [[Ucayali River|Ucayali]]
* [[Xingu River|Xingu]]
* [[Japurá River|Yapura]]
{{Multicol-end}}

