      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the Apollo mission|the film based upon it|Apollo 13 (film)|the Lovell-authored book called Apollo 13|Lost Moon}}
{{pp-protected|small=yes}}

{{Stack|
{{Infobox Space mission
