      </contributor>
      <minor />
      <comment>Reverted edit(s) by [[Special:Contributions/82.41.249.228|82.41.249.228]] identified as test/vandalism using [[WP:STiki|STiki]]</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox person
| name        = Alexander Selkirk
| image       = Alexander Selkirk Statue.jpg
| alt         = Statue of Alexander Selkirk in Lower Largo
| caption     = Statue of Alexander Selkirk in Lower Largo
| birth_date  = 1676
| birth_place = 
| death_date  = 13 December 1721
| death_place = 
